  "2026-05-10T21:15:14.302Z",codex-agent,"Workstreams completed 2026-05-10: (1) CLI dedup/perf hardening by introducing shared argv + levenshtein helpers and shared metadata normalizers used by create/update/bootstrap/commander/help/error/main; (2) search linked-corpus path optimized by resolving containment roots once and loading linked corpus entries concurrently; (3) observability hardening filters known starter-extension console-noise events/breadcrumbs in Sentry and release gate now reports ignored_noise counts/short IDs; (4) CI stability hardening adds npm-exec fallback for tarball smoke script; (5) docs dedup rewrote SDK and EXTENSIONS docs to one canonical section each; (6) remote validation executed over SSH on [redacted_ip]: Caddy + telemetry stacks healthy, rabbitmq queue depth 0 with consumer 1, telemetry event volumes present, public healthz 200 (redirect-follow), legacy /api/health still 404."
