  "2026-05-16T08:07:41.959Z",codex-audit,"Execution start 2026-05-16 follow-up: duplicate check reused pm-rnpb after pm context, pm search, pm list-open, and pm list-in-progress. Bootstrap passed: npm install -g ., pm --version 2026.5.14, node v25.9.0, pnpm 10.33.0, pnpm build. GitHub snapshot has no open issues and only Dependabot PRs #26/#24/#22 with pre-existing branch failures. Early agent-UX dogfood finding: pm get rejects --fields even though list/search support field narrowing; continuing with isolated temp-project dogfood, performance/code review, semantic/calendar/SDK/telemetry/Sentry/privacy review, scoped fixes, commit/push, and CI watch."
  "2026-05-16T08:17:04.115Z",codex-audit,"Audit evidence 2026-05-16 follow-up: isolated temp-project dogfood passed 44 workflows after adding get fields coverage; normal successful commands stayed around 422-469ms at the slow end, with linked test execution at 6301ms as expected. Implemented pm get --fields for low-token item metadata projection and exposed it through help, contracts, SDK action schema, and dogfood. Focused regression passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/get-append-command.spec.ts tests/integration/help-runtime.spec.ts tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts (47 tests). Full release gate passed with required telemetry/Sentry: coverage 92 files / 1304 tests at 100 percent, static/docs/typecheck/build/npx/npm-pack/compatibility ok, Sentry critical=1/high=4 within thresholds, telemetry finish_error_rate_pct=2.08 and zero missing error-code rows. Live telemetry stack health showed queue depth 0, rejected/publish errors 0, and fresh persisted events. pm health/validate report only the known five history drift warnings tracked under pm-xk39."
  "2026-05-16T08:29:51.787Z",codex-audit,"GitHub CI evidence 2026-05-16: pushed 81bde211e838997cb6c60af3516831b69e7af6dd and watched CI run 25957122629 to completion. All matrix jobs passed: ubuntu Node 20/22/24, macOS Node 20, and Windows Node 20. Ubuntu Node 20 completed the release-heavy path including coverage, static quality, compatibility migration, packaging smoke, npx tarball smoke, and Claude Code plugin smoke."
  "2026-05-16T16:15:24.700Z",maintainer-agent,"Audit session 2026-05-16 summary: (1) Merged Dependabot PRs #24 and #28 (production + dev deps); closed pm-2723. (2) Implemented positional title for pm create as pm-7vm9 — agents can now run 'pm create \"title\" --type X' without --title flag, with retry guidance. (3) Cleared 10 stale Sentry issues bound to v2026.5.10 (PM-CLI-N/H/K/J/M/F/D/G/E/C); only PM-CLI-A/9 ollama timeouts remain (tracked under pm-ibp7). (4) Cleaned pm-list.cpuprofile artifact and added *.cpuprofile/*.heapprofile/*.heapsnapshot to .gitignore. (5) Logged follow-up pm-hosd for pm init --with-packages flag. Performance baseline: pm --version 244ms, pm list 441ms, pm search 988ms — esbuild bundling (pm-gt82) remains the largest unrealized win."
